This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=5088

This is a pre-packaged version of the
http://github.com/vim-pandoc main plugins. Those are updated
versions of vimscript #3730.

It includes:

* vim-pandoc http://github.com/vim-pandoc/vim-pandoc
    + pandoc execution, through the :Pandoc command
    + omni completion (for bibliographic references)
    + advanced folding (normal, relative and stacked)
    + text formatting setup (auto formatting modes available)
    + etc.
* vim-pandoc-syntax http://github.com/vim-pandoc/vim-pandoc-syntax
    + syntax highlighting for pandoc markdown
* vim-pandoc-after http://github.com/vim-pandoc/vim-pandoc-after
    + third party plugins integration


